data.name: label2.Text
data.value: Karnıyarık, which reflects the great harmony of eggplant and meat, is one of the unchanging tastes of Turkish cuisine. Eggplants peeled and fried in a variegated manner; cooked with ingredients such as minced meat, tomato paste, onion and parsley, Karnıyarık is among the most delicious Turkish tastes served to the guests.
